00:36:48,174 --> 00:36:51,174
17 days of the worldwide event
has now begun.

480
00:36:51,544 --> 00:36:56,154
We will bring you all the best highlights
from the opening ceremony.

481
00:36:56,245 --> 00:37:01,365
The 2014 Winter Olympics in Sochi
has lifted its opening curtains.

